和独居老人。 ↑安娜·谢尔盖耶娃 另据报道，谢尔盖耶娃 6 月 10 日就已走马上任，其目前的工资比乌克兰总统泽连斯基还高出两倍不止。报道称，谢尔盖耶娃每月收入为 68600 格里夫纳（约 15605 人民币），而泽连斯基的官方收入仅为 28000 格里夫纳（约 6369 人民币）。 随着俄乌冲突持续，这一任命更引发了乌克兰人的质疑甚至是谩骂。「这是对人民的一记耻辱，作为乌克兰公民，我对此感到不安。」有网民说道。 目前，谢尔盖耶娃已将自己的社交账号 Instagram 账户设为非公开，乌克兰社会政策部也未对其任命进行更多的宣扬。25 岁「美容专家」成为乌克兰副部长，工资高过泽连斯基"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-2a0df652c260a34c791d5a09c3110e72_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "63 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/542841758"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Is8j8v8GO7TMQAxoIODI5MTM2NjQgzLuzlgYwFjj9AkAYcgk1NDI4NDE3NTh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1657743016.0695462", "card_id": "Q_542859060", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 158}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "成都 2022.7.12 号二批次土拍第一天上午就 5 宗熔断摇号，是否说明成都未来两三年房价是不会再跌了?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7184efe0a615003b8ce7136a20bd347c_1440w.jpg?source=172ae18b"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/542859060"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIs8j8v8GO7TMQAxoIODI5MTc0ODUg09izlgYwDzjQBEAZcgk1NDI4NTkwNjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1657743016.0701175", "card_id": "Q_539160459", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 69}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待 Wi-Fi 7 ？它会很快取代 Wi-Fi 6 吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-d1aa06bd1c9b393382a8409a07bc5487_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7